To use custom functions with the Essential Calculate component, you can extend its functionality by defining custom functions. Here's an example:

```csharp
using Syncfusion.Windows.Forms.Calculate;

public partial class Form1 : Form
{
    public Form1()
    {
        InitializeComponent();

